# Simple Chat Website

A Shopify Hydrogen storefront for simple-chat.com.

## Design Resources

**Figma Project**: https://www.figma.com/files/1565994570781438763/project/471089746

Use the Figma MCP to fetch designs when implementing UI components.

## Tech Stack

- **Framework**: Shopify Hydrogen (Remix-based)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Deployment**: Shopify Oxygen

## Key Directories

- `app/components/` - Reusable UI components
- `app/routes/` - Page routes (Remix file-based routing)
- `app/styles/` - Global styles and fonts
- `app/data/` - Data fetching utilities
- `app/graphql/` - Shopify GraphQL queries
